      "id": "PopularPost290730",
      "post_content": "Why on Earth did they print this in a core set? \"How to give every new player a completely wrongheaded understanding of delay-triggered abilities for the low low cost of ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol), ![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol). Oh, and did we mention we're packing a hefty set of cards with delayed-trigger abilities in the same set? YEAH! Go go gadget chaos!\"  \n  \nSundial is tech against one and only one competitive deck in the entire history of Magic: it hoses [High Tide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=High Tide) decks, turning their all-important [Reset](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reset) into a complementary [Time Walk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Walk). \"You wanted another untap phase? Here, have a whole 'nother turn!\" XD  \n  \nThis, [Final Fortune](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Final Fortune), [Last Chance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance), [Warrior's Oath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Oath), [Izzet Guildmage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Izzet Guildmage), [Nivix Guildmage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nivix Guildmage), [Gamble](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gamble), [Burning Wish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Wish), [Serum Powder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serum Powder).  \n  \nAnd [Darksteel Reactor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Reactor), or, whatever.  \n  \nYou will only actually... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost290730\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Why on Earth did they print this in a core set? \"How to give every new player a completely wrongheaded understanding of delay-triggered abilities for the low low cost of <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/>, <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Tap\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=tap&amp;type=symbol\"/>. Oh, and did we mention we're packing a hefty set of cards with delayed-trigger abilities in the same set? YEAH! Go go gadget chaos!\"<br/><br/>Sundial is tech against one and only one competitive deck in the entire history of Magic: it hoses <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"High Tide\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=High Tide\">High Tide</a> decks, turning their all-important <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reset\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reset\">Reset</a> into a complementary <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Time Walk\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Walk\">Time Walk</a>. \"You wanted another untap phase? Here, have a whole 'nother turn!\" XD<br/><br/>This, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Final Fortune\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Final Fortune\">Final Fortune</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Last Chance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance\">Last Chance</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Warrior's Oath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Oath\">Warrior's Oath</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Izzet Guildmage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Izzet Guildmage\">Izzet Guildmage</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nivix Guildmage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nivix Guildmage\">Nivix Guildmage</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gamble\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gamble\">Gamble</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burning Wish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Wish\">Burning Wish</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Serum Powder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serum Powder\">Serum Powder</a>.<br/><br/>And <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Darksteel Reactor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Darksteel Reactor\">Darksteel Reactor</a>, or, whatever.<br/><br/>You will only actually... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 290730)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '290730'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (1/17/2013 10:54:45 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall