      "id": "PopularPost176031",
      "post_content": "SO many possibilities for this card. Aside from the obvious of countering spells, you can evoke a creature like [Mulldrifter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mulldrifter) or [Shriekmaw](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shriekmaw) and then exile the sacrifice clause, or use it to keep various things from being sacrificed at the beginning of the next end step, such as the token from [Zektar Shrine expedition](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zektar Shrine expedition) or those from [Elemental mastery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elemental mastery) to amass a horde of elementals. Use it with [Glimmerpoint stag](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glimmerpoint stag) to permanently exile something, as well as other cards with the same type of wording. If you want to be cruel you can use this with [smokestack](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=smokestack) in order to add counters but skip the sacrifice effect. Brutal.",
