    {
      "id": "PopularPost273056",
      "post_content": "[Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason) etc etc etc: Read the card. It specifically says **\"this turn\" and \"until end of turn\" effects end** in the reminder text. This card is effective with cards that mention the \"end step\" *specifically*, like [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning) or [Last Chance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance), since it skips the end step.  \n  \nTL;DR: \"**Until end of turn**\" effects still trigger. \"**End step**\" effects do not. It's on the card, folks.  \n  \n@TheWrathofShane: \"Timmies\" aren't new players. Thanks for trying, though. A for effort.",
      "posted_by": "adrian.malacoda",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost273056\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Act of Treason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason\">Act of Treason</a> etc etc etc: Read the card. It specifically says  <b>\"this turn\" and \"until end of turn\" effects end</b> in the reminder text. This card is effective with cards that mention the \"end step\" <i>specifically</i>, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ball Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning\">Ball Lightning</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Last Chance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance\">Last Chance</a>, since it skips the end step.<br/><br/>TL;DR: \"<b>Until end of turn</b>\" effects still trigger. \"<b>End step</b>\" effects do not. It's on the card, folks.<br/><br/>@TheWrathofShane: \"Timmies\" aren't new players. Thanks for trying, though. A for effort.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '273056'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76402\">adrian.malacoda</span>\r\n                                (9/30/2012 10:32:04 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n       